    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Prakash Bettadapur</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/prakashbettadapur/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/af/PrakashBettadapur.jpg/240px-PrakashBettadapur.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/af/PrakashBettadapur.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PrakashBettadapur.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Prakash Bettadapur <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Prakash Bettadapur</b>,<br />\nan Indian American computer scientist, technologist, entrepreneur, advisor, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angel_investor\">angel investor</a>, and executive coach, active in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agile_software_development#Agile_management\">agile transformation</a>. \nPrakash Bettadapur holds a Proficience Certificate in computing systems from the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indian_Institute_of_Science\">Indian Institute of Science</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bangalore\">Bangalore</a>, a Bachelor's degree in electronics and telecommunications engineering from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Institute_of_Technology_Karnataka\">Karnataka Regional Engineering College</a>, India, and a Masters degree <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> in computing science from the <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a>, Canada, where he researched on <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">quiescence search</a> in computer chess under instructions of <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a>.  \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prakash_Bettadapur&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Prakash Bettadapur</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i>Experiments in Chess Capture Search</i>, M.Sc. Thesis, Department of Computing Science, <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a>.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Prakash Bettadapur</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i>Influence of Ordering on Capture Search</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#9_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICCA Journal, Vol. 9, No. 4</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Prakash Bettadapur</a>, <a href=\"/Tony_Marsland\" title=\"Tony Marsland\">Tony Marsland</a> (<b>1988</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0020737388800087\">Accuracy and Savings in Depth-Limited Capture Search</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/journals/ijmms/ijmms29.html\">International Journal of Man-Machine Studies, Vol. 29</a>, No. 5</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prakash_Bettadapur&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/prakashbettadapur/\">Prakash Bettadapur | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ammasprakash\">Prakash Bettadapur (@ammasprakash) / Twitter</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/prakashbettadapur\">Prakash Bettadapur presentations | SlideShare</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Prakash_Bettadapur&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/prakashbettadapur/\">Prakash Bettadapur | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Prakash Bettadapur</a> (<b>1986</b>). <i>Experiments in Chess Capture Search</i>, M.Sc. Thesis, Department of Computing Science, <a href=\"/University_of_Alberta\" title=\"University of Alberta\">University of Alberta</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Bettadapur:Prakash.html\">dblp: Prakash Bettadapur</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228230055\